A brief history

I'm a full-stack software engineer, I enjoy tackling complex problems. My main focus is on JavaScript/TypeScript, React, Node.js, and I also specialize in both NoSQL and SQL databases.

My daily playground? TypeScript/JavaScript, React, and Node.js. Recently, I work on a product called DeClustor, is an open-source cloud management B2B-focused platform that simplifies the deploying and monitoring of applications running on AWS ECS.

Out of work you can catch me meditating through outdoor runs, fusing Thai-Italian fusion cuisine in kitchen lab, experimenting with AI-enhanced home automation, or shredding the slopes on my snowboard when winter comes.

Growing up in Thailand taught me the value of adaptability and collaboration, which I bring to every team I work with.

I am a hard worker, I get things done without giving up
